42
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,070
If it really doesn't work out, I...

43
00:02:57,070 --> 00:02:58,130
Come to me anytime.

44
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:19,630
Do you feel wronged?

45
00:03:20,260 --> 00:03:20,890
No.

46
