amazing hospitality in the future.

152
00:07:21,390 --> 00:07:24,240
Yours sincerely, Marcos Yang.

153
00:07:27,180 --> 00:07:29,120
It is my pleasure.

154
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,680
You deserve it.

155
00:07:32,110 --> 00:07:35,040
Thanks to Marcos and you.

156
00:07:37,780 --> 00:07:39,130
Thank you so much.

157
00:07:47,710 --> 00:07:55,930
[Internal Office] [Convention Center]

158
00:07:49,450 --> 00:07:50,720
I'm looking forward for a strong

159
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:52,980
