161
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:59,460
Ms. Xu, it's very nice to meet you.

162
00:07:59,610 --> 00:08:01,160
Hope to see you again.

163
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:02,920
Definitely. We've just signed the contract

164
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:05,050
