196
00:10:03,270 --> 00:10:04,030
With an attitude like hers,

197
00:10:04,030 --> 00:10:05,720
I really can't work with her.

198
00:10:05,740 --> 00:10:07,100
If it really doesn't work out, I...

199
00:10:07,100 --> 00:10:08,230
Contact me anytime.

200
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,890
Postcard.

201
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,700
If you want to be like before,

202
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:27,440
you have to live more
strongly than anyone else.

203
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,740
You have to learn how to climb higher,

204
00:10:28,740 --> 00:10:30,410
learn how to fight,
and learn how to take what's yours.

205
00:10:30,410 --> 00:10:31,840
You must make everyone
who looked down on you

206
00:10:30,610 --> 00:10:33,710
[Young Lu Zhenzhen]

207
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:32,720
