to get justice for her.

229
00:11:34,530 --> 00:11:35,330
That's right.

230
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:37,350
We promise not to disturb Sister Feifei,

231
00:11:37,350 --> 00:11:38,950
but we must get revenge.

232
00:11:40,190 --> 00:11:42,330
You three can't go up
to the presidential suite.

233
00:11:42,330 --> 00:11:43,510
You need to swipe a card to go up,

234
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:45,120
